node.text:
Hey guys,

Here is my race recap from the weekend.
Guys I am always going to say what’s on my mind and tell it how it is. I might not always be right and I’ll be the first to admit it but I’ll never hold back on how I feel and you will guys will always get the truth from me. No hiding in group chats half truths or dms.
Thanks for all the support and messages I am giving it my everything during the week and on the weekend 

See you all at pala.

node.text:
Alright Alright here we go guys.
I was going to wait but I was thinking the redbud crowd is gonna need a little more time and as much heads up to beat the crowd at high point for the #jettsonbanner comp. high point set the bar pretty high.
Let’s go guys use the hashtag so I can keep track and see them all even if you guys can’t make the race love to see them who knows I might send something out to the best one online.
Winner gets my @alpinestars second moto race jersey delivered personally by me.
And I’ll give as many @ride100percent goggles as I can to the runner ups.
Image @alecgaut
